text:
Self-Evaluation Questionnaire


Thank you for making your word ratings. Please think back to the last word you repeated aloud for 20 second. Take a moment to think how you felt after repeating the word? To respond, please rate each statement below by clicking on a number from 1 to 7, whereby 1 = you strongly disagree with the statement, while 7 = you strongly agree with the statement.
I felt I'd let myself down
